 thead tr td { cursor:pointer; }

 .warning_pulse_timed { animation:warningPulse 0.5s linear infinite alternate; }
 .wrapper { direction:ltr; padding-bottom:125px; } 

 .slider {
    -webkit-animation:slide 1s forwards;
    animation:slide 0.75s forwards;
 }

 .slider_reverse {
    -webkit-animation:slideBack 1s forwards;
    animation:slideBack 0.75s forwards;
 }

 @-webkit-keyframes slide {
        0%   { left:-60%; }
        100% { left:0; }
 }

 @keyframes slide {
        0%   { left:-60%; }
        100% { left:0; }
 }

 @-webkit-keyframes slideBack {
        0%   { left:0; }
        100% { left:-60%; }
 }

 @keyframes slideBack {
        0%   { left:0; }
        100% { left:-60%; }
 }

 @-webkit-keyframes arrowBounce {
        0%   { left:0; }
        100% { left:25px; }
 }

 @keyframes arrowBounce {
        0%   { left:0; }
        100% { left:25px; }
 }

 @-webkit-keyframes warningPulse {
        0%   { left:0; }
        100% { left:25px; }
 }

 @keyframes warningPulse {
        0%   { box-shadow:0 0 0 orange; }
        100% { box-shadow:0 0 25px orange; }
 }
